Z : forward (z-axis +)
S : backwards (z-axis -)
Q : left (x-axis -)
D : right (x_axis +)
A : up (y-axis +)
E : down (y-axis -)

RMB + any of the above : rotate the camera

LMB on an object : select the object

t : initiates a translation
r : initiates a rotation
any number : indicates an amount (3 digits max)
v : specifies the x coord
b : specifies the y coord
n : specifies the z coord
SPACE : performs the transformation
